text: Don't miss out on this wonderful 1905 craftsman house in the Lettered Streets neighborhood. Fabulous 9'4 ceilings on the main level gives a spacious feel to the open plan living room, dining area. The kitchen and laundry room includes all appliances. This home has lots of original features, so bring your design ideas and enhance these lovely details. 1 bedroom and a full bathroom on the main level and 3 bedrooms with vaulted ceilings, and another full bathroom are on the second level. Large, partially fenced yard, with off street parking. Perfectly located for walking to nearby Elizabeth, Fouts and Battersby Field parks, and walking distance to the restaurants, bars and shops of Downtown Bellingham, and Squalicum Harbor.

Brand NEW Marlette home at Ponderosa Estates! Affordability and a gorgeous location minutes from Birch Bay! Appealing 23 acre park with a very northwest vibe. This new 3 bed, 2 bath home features a primary en-suite with spacious walk-in closet, dual sinks and ample storage. Bright contemporary kitchen with large pantry, gorgeous countertops with tile back splash and brand new stainless steel appliances. A spacious backyard where you can create your own garden and patio area. Watch the sunrise from your beautiful covered front porch. Take a walk down to the beach and enjoy cafes, restaurants, parks, trails and spectacular sunsets on the promenade. An all age year-round community.

Discover unparalleled waterfront living in this stunning, custom Bay-front estate, an architectural gem of the Pacific NW. Captivating saltwater and island views - & no powerlines - unlike any you've seen. Rare direct access to miles of beach from the backyard. Located just 4.5 miles from downtown Bellingham, 6 miles from PeaceHealth Medical Center. Luxuriate in the stunning Chef's kitchen, Spa-like Primary Suite, or any of the interior spaces & exquisite finishes of Doug Fir & artisan stonework. Multiple guest suites upstairs + a luxurious ADU your guests will absolutely LOVE, or use it as the ultimate home office with its separate entrance & garage. Radiant floor heat, brand new roof, zoned sprinklers + more. Owner Financing negotiable.

One of the best priced homes in Whatcom County! Cozy 1 bedroom cottage on a quiet cul de sac. Home will require some TLC but has great potential and room for your finishing touches. Private lot with shop space and shed for storage. Embrace rustic tranquility out in Maple Falls!

Imagine coming home by driving through a low-traffic street to arrive at your cul-de-sac destination. Park in the 2 car garage with extra storage, and walk into a lovely 3 bedroom turn-key home with fresh paint. As you prepare dinner in the large kitchen with an island and nook, you can utilize the brand-new stove & microwave. Move into the dining room featuring vaulted ceilings! Slider off-kitchen leads to a nice covered back patio where you can look over the mature landscaping and huge yard for games and gardening. End the night with relaxation in the living room where you can enjoy the gas fireplace with spaciousness for entertaining. This neighborhood is in high demand, and next to amazing schools. Don't miss out!

Welcome to your dream lakeside retreat! Enjoy unparalleled privacy on the serene, less crowded end of the lake, perfect for peaceful escapes and unforgettable gatherings. Create lasting memories with water sports, marshmallow toasting, and fishing. The property features a charming creek, a main house with 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths, 2 wood-burning fireplaces, a pool table, and a vintage bar. A separate cozy cabin offers a kitchen, laundry, bathroom, and outdoor BBQ space. A private dock and huge flat grassy area by the lake is ideal for games and relaxation. An extra lot adds over an acre of trees for seclusion. Enjoy quiet mornings and stunning sunsets, stargazing, and watching bald eagles' fish. Just a short drive to Bellingham and Seattle!

Great opportunity to own this completely updated charming home. Spacious bright kitchen with lots cabinets for storage, large living room, new double pane windows, new flooring, new paint, new Led lighting, new decks, move in ready. All new appliances all include. Extra parking space, storage shed included. Located in a close distance to town amenities, grocery stores and downtown. Buyer must be approved by the park before closing. This is a Must see!!

An easy simple downsize for anyone seeking quiet refuge & more time to do things that matter. Welcome home to a kinder, more carefree way to live. Ideal for nature lovers & golf enthusiasts. Perfectly situated--south-facing sunshine all day! Great design with vaulted ceilings & wonderful windows. This spaciously gracious home offers top-of-the-line finishes, gas fireplace, stainless appliances, excellent exterior decks & lots of storage. Walking distance to all amenities-a best value property!

Immaculate, turn-key weekend getaway cabin! Fully furnished (down to the dishes), sleeps four with sofa bed. A writer's retreat, a place of tranquility for creativity, a place to sail, swim & hike- you've found it. Excellent investment opportunity with a two bd. septic so you can expand on this large 1/3 of an acre lot. Easy-care gorgeous no-mow native landscape & a short walk to the swimming lake, boat launch & beach, a great location! A classic style featuring a wrap-around porch, high open ceilings w/ skylights, garden window & clean lines throughout. You will be impressed by the love & care that shine through! The lower level includes a laundry room, workspace, and storage for your kayak & outdoor equipmentsimple living at its finest.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District, Lummi High School

text: Here's your opportunity to own a townhome-style condo walkable to Fairhaven, with access to the Interurban Trail right outside your door. Hardwood floors throughout main living area and kitchen. Vaulted ceilings with skylights create a spacious airy feel. Beautifully renovated kitchen with a gas range, granite countertops and a custom sink. A private deck right off the living room, plumbed for gas and ready for your barbecue. In addition, step outside from the primary bedroom to a lovely private patio surrounded by nature. The second bedroom can also function as an office or a media room, with a convenient built-in Murphy bed. This unit has 2 garage parking spots, plus one assigned outdoor spota rare feature!

Welcome to your dream home nestled in the Samish Hill Neighborhood of Bellingham near Lake Padden, WWU, Fairhaven and Downtown. This exquisite, custom-built, 3bd/1.75ba home designed by Deborah Todd has an abundance of charm and elegance. This lovely, 2193 sq ft home offers unparalleled local craftsmanship & thoughtful touches throughout, including Brazilian cherry floors, as well as warm, rustic alder & walnut cabinetry. Huge windows flood the home with natural light. Enjoy the spacious fenced garden space with raised beds and room for RV parking and huge 2 car garage. Large lot offers potential room to build up to two 1000 sq ft ADUs presenting an exciting opportunity for additional living space or rental income.

Uncover the potential in this 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom cosmetic fixer. This 2-story home boasts a single-car garage, natural gas heat, and a new hot water heater, providing the convenience of all city services including water and sewer. Embrace the final days of summer by grilling your favorites on the patio or taking a leisurely stroll to the community park. With a little sweat equity, you can turn this property into your dream home, relishing a low-maintenance, easy-care lifestyle in a prime location just off Portal Way with no through streets. Don't miss this opportunity to make this property your own!

First time ever on the market! This 1959 rambler sits on nearly an acre of manicured property and features 3 bedrooms on the main floor, Chuckanut Bay views, and the potential to be your future dream home! The daylight basement is currently set up as a 2 bedroom ADU, but could easily be used as a family room and 4th and 5th bedroom. This home has been very well maintained, and is ready for the next owner to make it their own! The kitchen has been updated with new cabinets, flooring, and Corian countertops. Outside you will find the oversized two-bay shop with plenty of room for two vehicles, a workshop, and is plumbed for a half bath. There is also a 10x10 propane and storage shed. The options are endless as to what can be done!

Architecturally exciting, contemporary 3 bed. home on coveted west side w/ sweeping water & island westerly views! This gorgeous home offers everything in one package; sustainability, luxury & access to the water & outer islands just one block from home (professionally installed mooring buoy to convey with sale). A plethora of very recent upgrades include; all windows ('23), siding('23), commercial-grade carpet ('23), Swedish firebox ('23), solar panel installation ('23), heat-pump &mini-splits throughout home ('23), new roof ('21). This home has nearly zero cost energy-wise with the solar electric connected to the heating systems. Automatic generator w/dedicated propane tanks. Plus, one car garage with workshop + addl' storage building.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District, Lummi High School

text: Shangri-la in Cornwall Park Neighborhood! This meticulously renovated, 1460 sq ft, 3 bed, 2 bath home has it all. Front includes private patio w/serene landscaping & pavers that wrap around the home. Step inside to timeless hardwood & fir, cozy living area w/gas fireplace & sun-drenched dining room. Kitchen features granite countertops, cherry cabinets, stainless appliances including farmhouse sink, tile backsplash & floors. 2 bdrms & bath on main. Large primary upstairs w/multiple closets, & huge bath suite w/ soaker tub, tiled shower & skylight. Big basement w/ W/D & tons of storage. Private oasis in fenced & hardscaped backyard that includes outdoor shower, hot tub, firepit area, storage & finished garage. Paved alley parking spot.
neighborhoods: Broadway Park Historic District, Cornwall Park

text: Discover this 4-bedroom farmhouse set on 33 picturesque acres, offering a perfect blend of pasture and parklike grounds. Nestled on a quiet road with stunning Mt. Baker views, this property boasts a large hip roof barn and a versatile layout with a primary bedroom on the main floor. The partially wooded landscape provides privacy and tranquility, making it an ideal retreat. With its expansive acreage and potential for division, this property is ripe with possibilities. Embrace country living in this serene, private setting. Dont miss out on this unique opportunity!

Welcome to this quintessential Pacific Northwest craftsman on a quiet cul-de-sac in a well-established east-side neighborhood. Prepare to be greeted by a spacious living room with tall ceilings, a large kitchen & dining area that looks out to a fenced backyard, & a spacious covered patio, ideal for entertaining. This 2300+ home has a seamless flow & space for all, including 2 bedrooms on the main level, two bedrooms, & a bonus room upstairs. The main level primary suite offers a beautiful tiled walk-in shower & a large walk-in closet. Custom details include granite countertops, Knotty Alder solid core doors, trim & custom cabinets, an oversized garage, and a storage shed. Enjoy easy, comfortable living here.

Turn key, charming ground-level condo with Mt. Baker Views! Welcome to this spacious and wall-maintained 2-bed 1-bath condo, perfectly positioned on the ground floor with no stairs for easy access. The large windows flood the home with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. Featuring a stunning Mt. Baker view from the back patio. Newer carpet and paint throughout. Enjoy the breathtaking sunrise views and the calming breeze from the patio. Convenient covered carport and storage directly in front of the front door. Private front patio deck and back patio space. Excellent location in the active and accessible community of Ferndale, just minutes from downtown!

Captivating bay & island views from this 2016-built Samish Hill craftsman. Originally constructed as a builder's own home, you'll notice exceptional workmanship and extra bells & whistles throughout. Also on the main level is a bedroom/office with a 3/4 bathroom across the hall. Upstairs, you will find three additional bedrooms with vaulted ceilings. On the lower level, a 675 SQFT bonus room with wet bar. An oversized 2-car garage allows space for storage or a workshop. The trail behind the home provides quick access to Lake Padden.

Welcome home to your single level, immaculately maintained, 3 bed 2 ba home with a flat driveway just inside Gate 3. Open layout for socializing in the newly renovated kitchen complete with modern cabinetry + incredible storage, quartz countertops, deep stainless sink & penny tile backsplash. Great room style layout opens to trex deck over looking a gated sunny garden space. Generous and bright primary bed w/ ensuite double sink bath + 2 closets & private access to the deck. Tall crawl space for endless storage!

This home is located in Fairhaven's Parkway Village 55 and better active community. If you have been looking for a community to connect w/ and experience all that South Bellingham has to offer, this is it! This prime Southside home boasts an enviable location, excellent walkability, and numerous updates. The home features a bright, south-facing open kitchen and main living area. Recent upgrades include a new roof, a 4 kW solar system, a heat pump w/AC, and fresh interior and exterior paint. A gardener's paradise with multiple raised beds, fruit trees, and berries. Backyard shed provides a home office or yoga studio.

Don't miss this onepriced to sell! Welcome to this spacious four-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home situated in a charming neighborhood. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhome

This home offers a perfect blend of relaxation and recreation.

This home is privately situated on a dead-end lane along the sought-after Lake Whatcom waterfront. This idyllic, quaint home is set back from the street along an enchanting winding path amongst lush, mature landscaping. The freshly painted home is in a cleared sunny area with a covered patio and garden shed beside the front entry. Inside, there are formal and informal dining and living rooms, along with a bar and absolutely stunning lake and mountain views. The kitchen is in the center of the main floor making this the absolutely perfect home for entertaining! Upstairs is the primary suite and a 2nd bed (currently an office). There's a large yard toward the lake with 50' of waterfront, a shared dock, fire pit patiomand kayak storage.

Discover unparalleled equestrian living in this stunning Colonial-style home in beautiful Whatcom County. This 3 bdrm, 3.5 bath residence on 14.55 level acres boasts luxurious finishes, hardwood & slate flooring, vaulted ceilings, and a Chef's kitchen. Enjoy cozy evenings by one of the 3 fireplaces, workout in the flex room, or entertain in the spacious living & family rooms. A covered back deck & balcony overlook the cross-fenced pastures. A second parcel has a run-in barn w/tack rm and an outdoor riding arena. It offers a 2 bdrm septic system & potential for a second residence. With its natural beauty & convenient location, this amazing property is perfect for those seeking a peaceful retreat without sacrificing modern amenities.

Discover a prime 3.2-acre piece of vacant land on Semiahmoo Drive. Improved property includes a survey with topo layout, septic system, Birch Bay Water and Sewer with meter, and water access via four spigots. Nestled among majestic Fir and Cedar trees, the property offers a gentle slope and optimal western sun exposure. Part of a 32-parcel stretch held by Washington States DNR until 2070, it promises stability under RCW 79.13. Enjoy potential filtered water views for your future build. A sustainable and serene haven awaits you.

Easy living in this low-maintenance, single-story delight in Portal Commons on a cul-de-sac. 3 bedrooms and 2 bath including private primary suite w/walk-in closet and full bath. Warm cherry laminate floors extend thru a large portion of the living space. In the kitchen find a sparkling set of stainless steel appliances and a view out the window and sliding door to a large, level yard that's partially fenced. Just waiting for you to entertain on the patio, plant a garden, you name it! Plenty of room in your 2 car garage for storage, vehicles, or toys. A short drive to Bellingham and less than a minute to be on I5. Close to everything yet tucked away from the hustle & bustle.

2024 NEW construction 2-story 1800 sq. ft home that has 2 bedrooms, office room, 2.25 bath, and a white modern kitchen. Walk into a very light and bright open concept floor plan with waterproof Luxury VP flooring, quartz counter tops, soft close cabinets that have plenty of storage. Access the deck from the dinning room to admire the PNW evergreen views. Enjoy the Glenhaven community amenities such as their club house, pool, parks, lakes w/boat launches, and hiking trailheads.

Mid-county private 8.8-acres with stunning 2-story colonial, impressive shop and views of Mt. Baker. The 2900 sq ft home features a bright interior with 3+ bedrooms, 4 baths with a spacious primary suite. As you enter, you are greeted by an open staircase, French doors that lead to an office/study and an expansive living room with white oak floors and a wood stove. Addt'l two rooms upstairs + storage. Picturesque tree-lined driveway with pasture along both sides, a fenced garden and orchard. The stick-built 48'x60' shop has ADU potential, previously used for owner's business. Sandy loam soil. Would be great for horses. This property offers endless opportunities for peaceful rural living and space for hobbies or entrepreneurial ventures.

Amazing condo in the heart of Bellingham, located close to amenities, entertainment, local farmers market, & I-5. This 5th story condo w/elevator access features new floors, light fixtures & paint. Natural light pours through the ample windows in this coveted corner unit. Open kitchen & dining w/newer appliances, cozy fireplace in living room is an excellent heat source for main part of home. Off the dining room is a balcony that gets nice sun during the day + overlooks Depot Market & downtown. Primary BR features reading nook & newly remodeled bath. The extra bedroom/office boasts French doors. This unit has a W/D & plenty of extra storage! Underground parking for your safety. A private, owner access only, common balcony loc. on 2nd floor.
neighborhoods: City Center Bellingham, Downtown District Bellingham

text: The value in this home is the 1/25th share in Calmor Cove Club on Lake Samish, the Northwest's premier original waterski park. Get the boat in the water! Ideal, remarkable location just 5 min off I-5, South Lake Samish exit. View of lake and mountains. New TPO roof, all updated electric, plumbing rehab 2024. So many recreational options! Private dock space available. Community water Lake Samish surface water. Home in need of updating. 2 BR, 1 full BA. Single space carport w/shed. Wood fireplace/stove. Full time or second home, all ages - no rentals. Low dues and low taxes! Welcome to Lake Samish!

This property has space to roam! At over 4, 300 square feet and close to a comfort station, this large corner lot is spacious and private feeling. With a 1989 trailer and big covered deck, this property is also perfect for entertaining. Also included is a shed (also with a metal roof) and a fire pit area. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

The perfect multifamily investment in growing and appreciating Blaine WA. Walking distance to Canadian border. Incredible income potential in 1 bed and 2 bed single level units with decks. Remodeled interiors are lovely. Large 11, 000 sf lot allows for so much flexibility for the future. 1, 400+ sf heated shop split into 4 separate rentable areas would make great storage for renters, additional income, and/or owner use. Rents are increasing in Blaine! This is a rare opportunity as a high income rental, partial owner occupy, or extended living residence with separate living areas. Address is actually 410 and 420 5th Street. Seller has assumable loan at low APR.

Discover this lovely single-story craftsman home in the Maple Ridge community. Upon entering, you'll find a spacious living area filled with natural light, ideal for relaxing or entertaining. The kitchen boasts ample counter space and storage, making meal preparation a breeze. The 4th bedroom can easily serve as a home office, study, or guest room. The master suite provides a peaceful retreat with its cozy bedroom, ensuite bathroom, and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a shared bathroom ensure there's plenty of space for everyone. Upstairs, the bonus room above the garage provides a private entertainment area, or extra storage space. Outside, the fully fenced backyard provides privacy and and space for outdoor activities.

Welcome to your cozy haven in one of Bellingham's premier all ages mobile home parks! This charming 2-bed, 2-bath residence built in 2004 offers not only comfortable living but also the convenience of an office space. Step into an inviting open-concept kitchen, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying everyday meals. The bath off the primary bedroom adds a touch of luxury and privacy. Nestled in a serene and quiet neighborhood, you'll relish peaceful evenings and weekends. Plus, with parks and amenities nearby, every convenience is within reach. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a viewing today!

Contemporary and eco-friendly, NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes feature, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Showings available between 12-3pm, 7dys a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes

Adorable beach Home w/ 50 feet of serene waterfront. 2 bedrooms 1.75 baths. Recent complete renovation of the entire home to highlight the views and enhance the interior comfort and elegance. Inviting open concept floor plan engage residents and guests with an open airy connection with the outdoors in any season. Loft master suite with private balcony. Private 2nd bedroom suite, and a flex space for your ideas. Wildlife abounds from the deck with Herons, Seals, Loons, Grey Whales, & Orcas! Stunning views of the Canadian Cascades, Pt Roberts, Mt. Constitution on Orcas & Sandy Point! Abundant raised bed gardens & fruit to enjoy in season. Fee simple, Not Leased Land. VRBO Potential. Mini-Split HVAC. Work/storage building, RV parking.
